        <bioghist id="ref5">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Civil engineer Alexander Johnston Cassatt served as president of the Pennsylvania Railroad (1899-1906). He was the brother of artist Mary Cassatt.</p>
        </bioghist>
